OOC: Yeah, I know I have to do all that stuff, but Vulois keeps 
getting many interuptions.

Vulois

Vulois started walking through the tunnels, calling back to the trio 
as he went.

"Don't get to far behind, or you will be lost forever!"
______________________________________________________________________
Trainers

Prebon let out a huge laugh.

"Excellent! You are going to be my best servant in a long time. 
Everyone excpet Blaze, who will stay here and look after Spears, will 
come secretly to my meeting with Ramulus. I know longer have the urge 
ton control the Maxis, just to destroy them. When I give the signal, 
we are all to attack and kill Ramulus. Do you remember who Ramulus 
is, Slayer? Do you have any memories of your past?"
